CHUBBY CHEESEBURGER.

31:07.560 --> 31:09.289
OH, FUCK ME !

31:09.300 --> 31:11.689
Okay, Sir,
was that one...

31:11.700 --> 31:13.691
OH, JESUS, MY HEAD !

31:13.700 --> 31:14.997
NATE ?

31:15.000 --> 31:16.558
OH, FUCK !

31:18.100 --> 31:19.249
NATE !

31:27.830 --> 31:30.253
NATE, ARE YOU OKAY ?

31:31.700 --> 31:34.954
OH, FUCK !

31:39.500 --> 31:42.594
Sir, I didn't get that,
can I take your order, please ?

31:48.560 --> 31:50.528
Hello, Sir ?

31:57.060 --> 31:58.994
YOU DRIVE.

31:59.000 --> 32:00.558
I'M...

32:00.560 --> 32:02.551
I'M GONNA
GET SOME AIR.

32:02.560 --> 32:04.096
AND MAKE A PHONE CALL.

32:04.100 --> 32:05.351
OKAY.

32:20.900 --> 32:22.822
Sir, I didn't get that, can you
please repeat your order ?

32:22.830 --> 32:23.990
SHUT UP.

32:31.500 --> 32:34.025
YEAH, IS DR. DIPAOLO IN ?

32:37.760 --> 32:40.558
YEAH, YEAH,
IT'S DEFINITELY AN EMERGENCY !

32:40.560 --> 32:41.754
Sir, can I take
your order please ?

32:41.760 --> 32:42.954
SHUT THE FUCK UP !

32:42.960 --> 32:45.053
Sir, I'm going to have to
contact the manager.

32:47.260 --> 32:48.796
I CAN'T BELIEVE
I'M DOING THIS.

32:48.800 --> 32:51.792
CAN'T WE AT LEAST
GO INSIDE ?

32:51.800 --> 32:54.018
I COULD
GET A SEAWEED WRAP

32:54.030 --> 32:55.952
WHILE I PRETEND
TO LISTEN TO YOU.

32:56.700 --> 32:58.224
THAT COULDN'T
BE HER.

32:58.230 --> 33:00.050
I'M EATING
YOUR PROTEIN BAR.

33:00.060 --> 33:02.494
MAYBE IT IS.

33:06.530 --> 33:08.623
THIS IS LIKE
EATING UPHOLSTERY.

33:10.300 --> 33:11.756
I KNEW IT.

33:11.760 --> 33:14.228
BERN COULDN'T GET ANYONE
THAT GOOD-LOOKING

33:14.230 --> 33:16.391
TO JUMP HIS SAGGY ASS.

33:22.600 --> 33:25.398
I THOUGHT YOU AND DAD
HAD AN "AGREEMENT"

33:25.400 --> 33:26.992
ABOUT THIS
SORT OF THING.

33:27.000 --> 33:28.752
WE DID.

33:28.760 --> 33:30.193
WE DO.

33:30.200 --> 33:32.452
ONLY THIS TIME,
HE BROKE ONE OF THE RULES.

33:32.460 --> 33:33.893
HE DIDN'T
TELL ME FIRST.

33:33.900 --> 33:37.051
OH, SO, YOU'RE NOT UPSET THAT
DAD'S FUCKING SOMEBODY ELSE.

33:37.060 --> 33:38.857
YOU'RE UPSET
THAT HE DIDN'T TELL YOU

33:38.860 --> 33:40.589
HE WAS FUCKING
SOMEBODY ELSE.

33:40.600 --> 33:42.192
THAT'S RIGHT.

33:42.200 --> 33:44.725
THE RULE IS, IF YOU STEP
OUTSIDE THE HOLY BONDS,

33:44.730 --> 33:46.618
YOU HAVE TO TELL
YOUR WIFE FIRST.

33:46.630 --> 33:48.598
OH.

33:48.600 --> 33:51.524
SO, SHE CAN LINE UP
SOME YOUNG HOTTIE OF HER OWN.

33:51.530 --> 33:53.589
( laughing )

33:59.200 --> 34:01.691
WELL, I GUESS
THAT SOUNDS FAIR.

34:03.630 --> 34:04.949
YOU HAVE OTHER RULES ?

34:04.960 --> 34:07.394
A WHOLE SLEW OF THEM.

34:07.400 --> 34:11.188
GO ON, TELL ME,
I'M CURIOUS.

34:15.360 --> 34:17.954
YOU CAN'T FUCK MY FRIENDS,
I CAN'T FUCK YOURS.

34:17.960 --> 34:20.258
NO FUCKING OF
MUTUAL FRIENDS.

34:20.260 --> 34:22.194
NEVER IN HAWAII.

34:22.200 --> 34:25.454
NEVER IN A HOTEL THAT
COSTS MORE THAN $300 A NIGHT.

34:25.460 --> 34:28.918
AND NEVER IN A HOTEL
THAT'S UNDER $75 A NIGHT.

34:28.930 --> 34:30.921
( laughing )

34:32.400 --> 34:33.992
NOT ON HOLIDAYS.

34:34.000 --> 34:36.355
AND THERE ARE OTHERS,

34:36.360 --> 34:38.328
I JUST CAN'T REMEMBER
ALL OF THEM AT THE MOMENT.

34:38.330 --> 34:39.490
WOW.

34:39.500 --> 34:41.024
IS ONE OF THEM,

34:41.030 --> 34:43.851
NEVER FUCK ANYBODY ELSE
IN FRONT OF YOUR KIDS ?

34:43.860 --> 34:45.191
OH, I GUESS NOT.

34:45.200 --> 34:47.122
SINCE THERE WAS THAT TIME THAT
I WATCHED YOU IN THE HOT TUB

34:47.130 --> 34:48.688
WITH SOME OLD GUY
WITH A HAIRY BACK.

34:48.700 --> 34:50.588
DARLING,
YOUR FATHER WAS THERE.

34:50.600 --> 34:52.989
AND THERE WAS ABSOLUTELY
NO PENETRATION,

34:53.000 --> 34:55.195
I CAN ASSURE YOU
OF THAT.

34:55.200 --> 34:56.758
YEAH, I'LL BET
THAT WASN'T YOUR CHOICE.

34:56.760 --> 34:58.751
AND YOU WERE SUPPOSED
TO BE IN BED.

35:01.260 --> 35:04.093
I WAS ONLY GONE
A COUPLE OF HOURS, RICO.

35:04.100 --> 35:07.490
EVERY HOUR YOU'RE GONE IS
AN HOUR I HAVE TO STAY LATE.

35:07.500 --> 35:09.718
I'M SORRY ABOUT
YOUR BUDDY'S KID,

35:09.730 --> 35:11.288
BUT I HAVE KIDS
OF MY OWN AT HOME.

35:11.300 --> 35:14.121
IS THIS ABOUT US NOT GIVING YOU
THE LOAN FOR THE HOUSE ?

35:14.130 --> 35:15.654
BECAUSE YOU NEVER
USED TO COMPLAIN

35:15.660 --> 35:17.457
ABOUT HAVING TO WORK
A LITTLE OVERTIME.

35:17.460 --> 35:20.554
THIS IS ABOUT ME NOT WANTING
TO BE TAKEN ADVANTAGE OF

35:20.560 --> 35:22.289
BY MY EMPLOYERS.

35:22.300 --> 35:24.120
WE'RE MORE THAN JUST
YOUR EMPLOYERS, RICO.

35:24.130 --> 35:25.995
THAT'S BULLSHIT, DAVID,
AND YOU KNOW IT.

35:26.000 --> 35:28.560
WHEN IT'S CONVENIENT,
WE'RE LIKE FAMILY.

35:28.560 --> 35:30.699
BUT IN A PINCH,
I'M JUST AN EMPLOYEE.

35:30.700 --> 35:33.191
AND YOU AND NATE
ARE JUST MY BOSSES.

35:34.330 --> 35:35.820
HEY, LITTLE LADY.

35:37.660 --> 35:38.797
TAYLOR,

35:38.800 --> 35:40.153
I TOLD YOU
TO WAIT UPSTAIRS.

35:40.160 --> 35:41.889
MY TUMMY HURTS.

35:41.900 --> 35:45.119
IS THAT MAN DEAD ?

35:49.160 --> 35:51.321
THAT MAN WAS
TOTALLY DEAD.

35:55.230 --> 35:57.698
YES, THAT MAN
WAS TOTALLY DEAD.

35:59.260 --> 36:00.625
DID YOU KILL HIM ?

36:00.630 --> 36:01.892
NO.

36:01.900 --> 36:04.494
DID THAT OTHER MAN
IN THERE KILL HIM ?

36:04.500 --> 36:05.421
NO.

36:05.430 --> 36:08.490
HE DIED OF
NATURAL CAUSES.

36:09.860 --> 36:11.589
MY FRIEND
RENEE SAID,

36:11.600 --> 36:13.898
SOONER OR LATER,
WE'LL ALL BE DEAD.

36:16.000 --> 36:17.490
THAT'S TRUE.

36:17.500 --> 36:20.799
SO, SOMEDAY I'LL BE DEAD
LAYING ON A TABLE LIKE THAT ?

36:20.800 --> 36:23.428
NOT FOR A VERY,
VERY LONG TIME.

36:24.260 --> 36:25.989
MY MOM SAYS

36:26.000 --> 36:28.753
MY DAD'S GOOD AS DEAD
AS FAR AS SHE'S CONCERNED.

36:29.660 --> 36:34.097
YES, WELL, THAT'S JUST HER WAY
OF EXPRESSING ANGER AT HIM

36:34.100 --> 36:37.228
FOR NOT BEING AROUND.

36:37.230 --> 36:41.348
SOMETIMES MY MOM SAYS
SHE WISHES SHE WAS DEAD.

36:43.830 --> 36:45.127
THAT'S JUST SOMETHING
THAT PEOPLE SAY

36:45.130 --> 36:47.951
WHEN THEY'RE UPSET
ABOUT SOMETHING.

36:49.030 --> 36:50.850
DID THAT DEAD MAN
IN THERE HAVE ANY KIDS ?

36:50.860 --> 36:52.327
YEAH.

36:52.330 --> 36:55.049
HE HAD A WIFE
AND THREE CHILDREN,

36:55.060 --> 36:56.994
AND FIVE GRANDCHILDREN.

36:57.000 --> 36:59.798
I DON'T EVER
WANNA DIE.

36:59.800 --> 37:02.360
ME, NEITHER.

37:08.800 --> 37:11.428
IT'S CALLED
ARTERIOVENOUS MALFORMATION.

37:11.430 --> 37:13.352
"AVM" FOR SHORT.

37:13.360 --> 37:16.796
LOTS OF PEOPLE
HAVE IT THEIR WHOLE LIVES
AND NEVER EVEN KNOW.

37:16.800 --> 37:18.688
AND THE PILLS ?

37:20.230 --> 37:22.494
ARE AN ANTI-SEIZURE
MEDICATION.

37:24.700 --> 37:26.588
SO, WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU,
THAT WAS A SEIZURE ?

37:26.600 --> 37:27.794
SORT OF.

37:27.800 --> 37:29.392
SORT OF ?

37:29.400 --> 37:31.152
IT WAS A MILD SEIZURE.

37:32.830 --> 37:35.196
DOES DAVID
KNOW ABOUT THIS ?

37:35.200 --> 37:36.519
YES, HE DOES.

37:36.530 --> 37:38.828
BUT I DON'T WANT MOM TO KNOW,
'CAUSE SHE'LL JUST FREAK OUT.

37:38.830 --> 37:41.298
IT'S NO BIG DEAL,
I PROMISE.

37:43.000 --> 37:45.355
YOU KNOW, PEOPLE
DON'T JUST SPAZ OUT

37:45.360 --> 37:48.227
AND HORK ALL OVER THEIR SHOES
FOR NO GOOD REASON, NATE.

37:48.230 --> 37:49.925
TWO WORDS.

37:49.930 --> 37:52.251
TOFU MEATLOAF.

37:53.530 --> 37:55.327
LOOK, BESIDES, NOW THAT
I HAVE THESE PILLS,

37:55.330 --> 37:56.558
IT'LL BE TOTALLY
UNDER CONTROL.

37:56.560 --> 37:58.596
YOU SWEAR ?

37:58.600 --> 38:00.022
I SWEAR.

38:00.030 --> 38:03.796
I JUST HAVE TO TAKE THEM
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE, IS ALL.

38:05.460 --> 38:07.553
I DON'T BELIEVE YOU.

38:07.560 --> 38:10.256
JUST DO ME A FAVOR AND DON'T
TELL DAVID ABOUT THIS, OKAY ?

38:19.930 --> 38:22.319
THIS CLIENT OF MINE
IS A PROSTITUTE.

38:22.330 --> 38:24.195
SO, IS THAT SUPPOSED
TO SHOCK ME ?

38:24.200 --> 38:25.724
WHAT ?

38:25.730 --> 38:28.995
GOD, NOT EVERYTHING
IS ABOUT YOU !

38:29.000 --> 38:31.719
YOU'RE SUCH
A CLASSIC NARCISSIST.

38:31.730 --> 38:34.255
BRENDA, JUST BECAUSE
YOUR PARENTS ARE SHRINKS,

38:34.260 --> 38:36.421
DOESN'T MEAN YOU KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT PSYCHOLOGY.

38:36.430 --> 38:38.091
AND JUST BECAUSE
YOU'RE A SHRINK,

38:38.100 --> 38:40.591
DOESN'T MEAN THAT YOU'RE NOT
OUT OF YOUR FUCKING MIND.

38:42.800 --> 38:46.190
YOU KNOW, I'VE TREATED SEVERAL
PROSTITUTES OVER THE YEARS.

38:46.200 --> 38:48.350
AND THEY'RE NOT AS
UNCOMMON AS YOU--

38:48.360 --> 38:50.123
OH!

38:52.530 --> 38:54.122
THAT'S HER ?

38:54.130 --> 38:56.826
SHE'S YOUR AGE.

38:57.560 --> 38:59.152
I HAVE TO TALK TO HER.

38:59.160 --> 39:00.923
OH, MOM, DON'T,
PLEASE, DON'T.

39:00.930 --> 39:03.228
WAIT, WAIT,
I'M NOT ANGRY.

39:03.230 --> 39:04.697
I'M NOT GONNA
MAKE A SCENE.

39:04.700 --> 39:06.952
I JUST NEED TO PERSONALIZE
THE EXPERIENCE

39:06.960 --> 39:08.598
AND HUMANIZE
THE SITUATION.

39:08.600 --> 39:10.227
IT'S FOR
ALL OF US.

39:10.230 --> 39:12.221
YOU'LL JUST
REGRET IT !

39:13.030 --> 39:14.588
MISS...

39:14.600 --> 39:16.329
OH, MISSY ?

39:17.600 --> 39:19.818
HELLO, I'M MARGARET,
BERN'S WIFE.

39:22.530 --> 39:26.022
I JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW
IT'S OKAY WITH ME.

39:26.030 --> 39:27.497
YOU KNOW WHAT,
I'D LOVE TO CHAT,

39:27.500 --> 39:28.853
BUT I'VE GOTTA GO
MEET BERN FOR LUNCH.

39:28.860 --> 39:31.727
( laughing )

39:31.730 --> 39:35.120
(female screaming )

39:36.030 --> 39:37.827
GET OFF, YOU BITCH !

39:37.830 --> 39:39.650
I CAN'T BELIEVE YOU !

39:44.230 --> 39:46.721
I'LL SEE YOU
IN HELL !

39:50.230 --> 39:52.095
I HOPE YOU
LIKE HERPES !

40:05.360 --> 40:08.193
YOU KNOW, I THOUGHT
SHE'D BE MORE EVOLVED.

40:08.200 --> 40:09.792
EVOLVED ?!

40:09.800 --> 40:12.291
MOTHER, YOU JUST
ATTACKED THAT WOMAN !

40:12.300 --> 40:13.358
REPEATEDLY.

40:13.360 --> 40:15.453
SHE COULD HAVE YOU
THROWN IN JAIL !

40:15.460 --> 40:17.348
I SERIOUSLY
DOUBT THAT.

40:20.400 --> 40:22.220
ARE YOU HUNGRY ?

40:22.230 --> 40:25.449
WHY AM I HERE ?

40:26.500 --> 40:29.025
WHY WAS IT NECESSARY
FOR ME TO BE HERE

40:29.030 --> 40:30.497
WITH YOU FOR THIS ?

40:30.500 --> 40:33.389
BECAUSE YOU NEEDED
A FUCKING AUDIENCE !

40:35.000 --> 40:37.150
NOT EVERYTHING'S
ABOUT YOU, BRENDA.

40:37.160 --> 40:38.058
LOOK AT MOMMY,

40:38.060 --> 40:39.948
ISN'T MOMMY PRETTY ?

40:39.960 --> 40:41.757
ISN'T MOMMY FABULOUS,

40:41.760 --> 40:43.318
AND FREE-SPIRITED,

40:43.330 --> 40:44.490
AND UNINHIBITED ?

40:44.500 --> 40:45.626
VALIDATE MOM MY, KIDS,

40:45.630 --> 40:47.598
BECAUSE SHE'S INCAPABLE
OF DOING IT HERSELF.

40:47.600 --> 40:49.591
NO WONDER BILLY
ENDED UP IN A PSYCH WARD,

40:49.600 --> 40:51.022
NOT THAT YOU CARE.

40:51.030 --> 40:53.248
FOR YOUR INFORMATION,
MISS HIGH AND MIGHTY,

40:53.260 --> 40:54.522
THIS IS LIFE.

40:54.530 --> 40:56.896
PEOPLE HAVE CRISES.

40:56.900 --> 40:58.299
THEY PUSH EACH
OTHER'S BUTTONS,

40:58.300 --> 41:00.393
THEY INFLICT PAIN
ON ONE ANOTHER.

41:00.400 --> 41:03.153
AND ONCE
IN A FUCKING BLUE MOON...

41:03.160 --> 41:05.594
THEY BRING OUT
THE BEST IN EACH OTHER.

41:05.600 --> 41:08.990
BUT MOSTLY,
THEY BRING OUT THE WORST.

41:11.200 --> 41:13.293
YOU'RE PATH ETIC.

41:13.300 --> 41:14.619
DON'T YOU DARE
JUDGE ME.

41:14.630 --> 41:17.326
YOU THINK YOU'RE THE PARAGON
OF MENTAL HEALTH ?

41:17.330 --> 41:18.399
JUST BECAUSE
YOU'VE BEEN DATING

41:18.400 --> 41:20.254
THE SAME MAN FOR
THE PAST FEW MONTHS ?

41:20.260 --> 41:23.559
THAT'S REAL, COMPARED TO WHAT
YOUR FATHER AND I HAVE ?

41:23.560 --> 41:25.391
YOU'RE JUST JEALOUS.

41:25.400 --> 41:26.958
OF WHAT ?

41:26.960 --> 41:29.155
THE FACT THAT
I HAVEN'T ALLOWED YOU

41:29.160 --> 41:32.197
TO TOTALLY DESTROY MY LIFE LIKE
YOU HAVE EVERYBODY ELSE'S !

41:32.200 --> 41:33.553
WHAT LIFE ?

41:33.560 --> 41:37.428
YOU'VE SPENT 32 YEARS

41:37.430 --> 41:39.648
BEING YOUR LITTLE
BROTHER'S NURSEMAID.

41:39.660 --> 41:40.797
OH, FUCK YOU !

41:40.800 --> 41:43.291
TO AVOID HAVING ANY
EMOTIONAL LIFE OF YOUR OWN.

41:43.300 --> 41:46.497
AND NOW
THAT HE'S BEEN PUT AWAY,

41:46.500 --> 41:49.628
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
FACE YOUR OWN DEMONS,

41:49.630 --> 41:51.052
AND SWEETHEART ?

41:51.060 --> 41:53.051
THEY'RE LEGION.

42:01.200 --> 42:03.851
GET OUT OF MY CAR.

42:06.100 --> 42:07.920
I WOULD BE HAPPY TO.

42:22.430 --> 42:24.751
I HOPE YOU LIKE PORK ROAST
AND MASHED POTATOES.

42:24.760 --> 42:26.625
THEY'RE OKAY.

42:28.160 --> 42:29.593
WHERE ARE YOU GOING,
DEAR ?

42:29.600 --> 42:31.295
TO WATCH TV.

42:31.300 --> 42:34.519
IN THIS HOUSE,
WE EAT DINNER AT THE TABLE.

42:34.530 --> 42:37.397
YOU DON'T WATCH TV
WHILE YOU EAT ?

42:37.400 --> 42:39.425
NO, WE DON'T.

42:39.430 --> 42:41.898
MAYBE WE CAN WATCH SOME TV
WHEN WE'RE DONE EATING.

42:48.560 --> 42:50.221
SO, WHAT GRADE
ARE YOU IN, TAYLOR ?

42:50.230 --> 42:51.652
FOURTH.

42:51.660 --> 42:53.423
OH!

42:53.430 --> 42:56.627
DAVID WAS IN
THE FOURTH GRADE ONCE.

42:58.330 --> 43:00.195
IT'S TRUE.

43:01.800 --> 43:05.099
DID YOU KNOW DAVID USED TO BE
MY UNCLE KEITH'S BOYFRIEND ?

43:07.200 --> 43:09.293
YES, I DID.

43:11.930 --> 43:13.420
SOMETIMES...

43:13.430 --> 43:15.796
MY MOMMA CALLS MY UNCLE KEITH
A PUNK-ASS FUDGE-PACKER.

43:15.800 --> 43:17.688
'CAUSE HE LIKES MEN
INSTEAD OF WOMEN.

43:17.700 --> 43:20.999
I GUESS THAT MAKES YOU
A PUNK-ASS FUDGE-PACKER,

43:21.000 --> 43:22.558
TOO, DON'T IT ?

43:22.560 --> 43:25.688
WE DON'T USE THOSE KINDS
OF WORDS AT THIS TABLE.

43:25.700 --> 43:28.498
IN FACT, WE DON'T USE
THOSE KINDS OF WORDS AT ALL.

43:28.500 --> 43:29.751
HOW COME ?

43:29.760 --> 43:31.819
WELL, BECAUSE
THOSE WORDS ARE--

43:31.830 --> 43:33.354
HATEFU L.

43:33.360 --> 43:34.827
THOSE ARE
HATEFUL WORDS.

43:34.830 --> 43:36.525
WHAT WORDS
DO YOU USE ?

43:40.160 --> 43:42.151
HOMOSEXUAL.

43:46.600 --> 43:48.158
MY UNCLE KEITH
HAS A NEW BOYFRIEND.

43:48.160 --> 43:49.718
HIS NAME'S EDDIE.

43:49.730 --> 43:52.699
HE DRIVES AN AMBULANCE,
BUT I DON'T LIKE HIM TOO MUCH.

43:52.700 --> 43:54.554
WHY NOT ?

43:54.560 --> 43:56.926
HE LOOKS AT HIMSELF
IN THE MIRROR A LOT

43:56.930 --> 43:59.296
AND HE TALKS TO ME
LIKE I'M STUPID.

43:59.300 --> 44:01.052
I'M SURE
THAT'S NOT TRUE.

44:01.060 --> 44:02.857
YES, IT IS.

44:02.860 --> 44:05.829
WELL, IT IS TRUE.

44:05.830 --> 44:10.028
SOME PEOPLE JUST DON'T KNOW
HOW TO TALK TO CHILDREN.

44:11.230 --> 44:12.697
TELL ME ABOUT IT.

44:20.900 --> 44:22.959
I THINK
I'LL START THE DISHES.

44:38.030 --> 44:40.726
( Lisa )
IT'S TIME FOR YOU
TO LEAVE NOW !

44:40.730 --> 44:41.890
GO!

44:44.760 --> 44:45.988
GO!

44:48.730 --> 44:50.288
GO!

44:50.300 --> 44:52.120
GO!

44:54.630 --> 44:56.427
IS EVERYTHING OKAY ?

44:56.430 --> 44:58.921
OH, CLAIRE, I THOUGHT
YOU WERE TAKING A NAP.

44:58.930 --> 45:01.023
I WAS READING.

45:01.030 --> 45:03.225
WHERE'S NATE ?

45:03.230 --> 45:05.721
HE'S OUTSIDE
MAKING A PHONE CALL.

45:07.960 --> 45:10.349
WHO WERE
YOU TALKING TO ?

45:12.100 --> 45:13.249
ANTS.

45:13.260 --> 45:15.023
I'M BEING
OVERRUN BY THEM.

45:15.030 --> 45:17.851
AT FIRST I TRIED SETTING
A LITTLE FOOD ASIDE FOR THEM

45:17.860 --> 45:19.088
NEXT TO THE BACK DOOR.

45:19.100 --> 45:21.921
THEN I TRIED COAXING THEM OUT
WITH SOME CITRUS OIL.

45:21.930 --> 45:24.319
NOW I'M TRYING
TO REASON WITH THEM.

45:27.100 --> 45:28.954
AT HOME, MY DAD USED TO SQUIRT
THEM WITH LIGHTER FLUID

45:28.960 --> 45:30.655
AND TORCH THEM.

45:34.800 --> 45:37.724
I'M NOT STILL
IN LOVE WITH YOUR BROTHER,

45:37.730 --> 45:39.322
IF THAT'S
WHAT YOU'RE THINKING.

45:39.330 --> 45:42.026
ACTUALLY, I WASN'T
THINKING THAT.

45:44.400 --> 45:46.049
I USED TO BE.

45:46.060 --> 45:50.099
I USED TO THINK ONE DAY HE WOULD
REALIZE I WAS THE ONE FOR HIM.

45:50.100 --> 45:52.557
BUT HE NEVER HAS.

45:55.160 --> 45:56.718
DO YOU THINK
HE EVER WILL ?

45:56.730 --> 46:01.451
I'M PROBABLY NOT THE PERSON
TO BE ASKING THAT QUESTION.

46:03.200 --> 46:04.929
HE'S MY BROTHER AND ALL,
BUT TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH,

46:04.930 --> 46:06.591
I'M JUST GETTING
TO KNOW THE GUY.

46:08.430 --> 46:10.819
WELL, HE'S A HEARTBREAKER,
THAT'S FOR SURE.

46:10.830 --> 46:14.721
THERE ARE A DOZEN WOMEN
ALL OVER SEATTLE WHO WOULD FREAK

46:14.730 --> 46:16.254
IF THEY KNEW
HE WAS BACK HERE.

46:16.260 --> 46:19.252
YOU MUST THINK
I'M SO STUPID.

46:19.260 --> 46:21.194
NO, I DON'T.

46:23.430 --> 46:24.692
DO YOU
HAVE A BOYFRIEND ?

46:24.700 --> 46:25.951
NO.

46:25.960 --> 46:29.088
NOT ANYMORE.

46:30.600 --> 46:32.852
WE BROKE UP.

46:34.130 --> 46:35.825
YOU'RE BETTER OFF,
TRUST ME.

46:38.160 --> 46:40.151
FUCKIN' ANTS.

46:40.160 --> 46:42.594
I JUST WANTED TO HEAR
HOW YOUR DAY WENT.

46:42.600 --> 46:45.797
MY MOTHER PRACTICALLY
BEAT THE SHIT OUT OF A WOMAN

46:45.800 --> 46:47.119
IN A PARKING LOT,

46:47.130 --> 46:48.597
but apart from that,
I'm fine.

46:48.600 --> 46:50.056
How's Seattle ?

46:50.060 --> 46:52.290
SEATTLE'S GOOD.

46:52.300 --> 46:53.324
WHAT'S THIS
ABOUT YOUR MOTHER

46:53.330 --> 46:54.752
TRYING TO BEAT THE SHIT
OUT OF SOMEBODY ?

46:54.760 --> 46:57.194
OH, I REALLY DON'T FEEL LIKE
RELIVING IT RIGHT NOW.

46:57.200 --> 46:59.589
HOW'S IT GOING
WITH CLAIRE ?

46:59.600 --> 47:02.819
YEAH, GREAT,
WE'RE GETTING ALONG GREAT.

47:05.400 --> 47:06.822
IS EVERYTHING OKAY ?

47:06.830 --> 47:10.357
NO, I JUST
HAVE A HEADACHE.

47:12.530 --> 47:14.896
WE'RE GONNA HIT THE ROAD
FIRST THING IN THE MORNING.

47:14.900 --> 47:17.425
OKAY, WELL,
I'LL SEE YOU THEN.

47:17.430 --> 47:19.227
Yep.

47:20.300 --> 47:23.451
LISTEN, NATE, I JUST RAN A BATH
AND IT'S GETTING COLD, SO...

47:24.500 --> 47:26.092
I MISS YOU.

47:28.230 --> 47:30.357
I MISS YOU, TOO.

48:00.860 --> 48:02.919
( knocking )

48:13.260 --> 48:14.921
HEY.

48:14.930 --> 48:16.921
HI.

48:18.600 --> 48:20.955
YOU NEVER CALLED.

48:23.100 --> 48:24.829
HOW DID YOU KNOW
WHERE I LIVE ?

48:24.830 --> 48:26.252
WELL...

48:26.260 --> 48:29.229
THAT'S REALLY
NOT IMPORTANT.

48:30.700 --> 48:33.999
I THINK MAYBE IT IS.

48:36.430 --> 48:38.728
YOU WANNA KNOW
WHAT'S REALLY IMPORTANT ?

48:41.700 --> 48:43.691
SHOW ME.

49:04.030 --> 49:08.729
( moaning )

49:27.430 --> 49:29.125
SHE GIVE YOU
A HARD TIME ?

49:29.130 --> 49:32.293
NOT REALLY.

49:34.600 --> 49:37.160
LET ME GRAB HER
AND WE'LL GET OUT OF YOUR WAY.

49:45.300 --> 49:46.790
THAN KS, AGAIN.

49:46.800 --> 49:49.018
IT'S NO PROBLEM
WHATSOEVER, SHE'S...

49:49.030 --> 49:51.919
SHE'S A GREAT KID, KEITH,
SHE REALLY IS.

49:51.930 --> 49:54.228
CONSIDERING EVERYTHING
SHE'S BEEN PUT THROUGH,

49:54.230 --> 49:55.754
IT'S KIND OF A MIRACLE.

49:57.530 --> 49:58.895
WELL, WE SHOULD GO.

50:05.760 --> 50:06.897
OH, YEAH.

50:09.500 --> 50:10.956
GOODNIGHT, DAVID.

50:18.430 --> 50:20.159
( door closing )

50:34.230 --> 50:35.891
( door opening )

50:37.700 --> 50:39.554
I THOUGHT YOU MIGHT
NEED AN EXTRA QUILT.

50:41.030 --> 50:42.793
IT GETS COLD
IN THIS ROOM.

50:42.800 --> 50:45.018
THAN KS, LISA.

50:49.630 --> 50:51.393
ARE YOU OKAY ?

50:51.400 --> 50:52.321
YEAH.

50:52.330 --> 50:54.594
I'M FINE.

50:54.600 --> 50:55.726
ARE YOU SURE ?

50:55.730 --> 50:57.823
YEAH, I'M GOOD.

50:59.900 --> 51:01.424
YOU CAN'T FOOL ME, NATE.

51:01.430 --> 51:03.728
I KNOW YOU TOO WELL.

51:05.600 --> 51:07.090
I'M FINE.

51:17.060 --> 51:20.826
( sobbing )

51:22.330 --> 51:24.594
OH, POOR BABY.

51:24.600 --> 51:26.750
IT'S OKAY.

51:26.760 --> 51:28.728
I'M HERE.

51:28.730 --> 51:31.028
I'M RIGHT HERE.

51:31.960 --> 51:34.190
IT'S OKAY.

51:49.400 --> 51:51.220
ARE YOU SURE YOU DON'T
WANT ANY BREAKFAST ?

51:51.230 --> 51:52.322
OH, NO, I'M GOOD.

51:52.330 --> 51:53.627
I NEVER
EAT BREAKFAST.

51:53.630 --> 51:57.259
LISA, HAVE YOU SEEN
MY OLD BROWN FLANNEL SHIRT ?

51:57.260 --> 52:00.821
I'M PRETTY SURE IT GOT DONATED
TO THE CO-OP GARAGE SALE.

52:00.830 --> 52:01.990
NO...

52:02.000 --> 52:04.457
HERE IT IS.

52:06.360 --> 52:08.021
OH, I LOVE THAT SHIRT.

52:08.030 --> 52:09.793
IT'S SO NATE.

52:11.960 --> 52:13.427
WHY DON'T YOU
HANG ONTO IT ?

52:13.430 --> 52:14.692
NO, I COULDN'T.

52:14.700 --> 52:17.225
NO, COME ON,
I WANT YOU TO HAVE IT.

52:17.230 --> 52:18.788
IT'S YOUR SHIRT,
WHAT WOULD I WANT WITH IT ?

52:18.800 --> 52:20.051
WOULD YOU
JUST KEEP IT ?

52:23.360 --> 52:25.021
WE SHOULD PROBABLY
HIT THE ROAD.

52:25.030 --> 52:26.657
WE'VE GOT TO PICK UP
MR. MOSSBACK.

52:26.660 --> 52:28.218
RIGHT.

52:30.600 --> 52:32.022
LISA ?

52:32.030 --> 52:34.396
AS ALWAYS,
IT'S BEEN GREAT...

52:34.400 --> 52:36.288
SEEING YOU.

52:36.300 --> 52:37.995
TAKE CARE
OF YOURSELF, NATE.

52:38.000 --> 52:40.025
YOU, TOO.

52:41.860 --> 52:43.020
IT WAS NICE
TO MEET YOU.

52:43.030 --> 52:45.498
NICE MEETING YOU,
CLAIRE.

52:53.700 --> 52:55.019
THAN KS.

53:03.830 --> 53:05.388
MORNING, MOM.

53:06.230 --> 53:09.051
IT'S AWFULLY QUIET AROUND HERE
WITH NATE AND CLAIRE BEING GONE.

53:09.060 --> 53:11.722
I SUPPOSE IT IS.

53:13.330 --> 53:16.891
WHAT TIME DID YOUR FRIEND
COME BY TO PICK UP HIS NIECE ?

53:16.900 --> 53:19.494
HALF PAST ONE.

53:19.500 --> 53:23.049
THAT'S AWFULLY LATE FOR
A CHILD HER AGE TO BE UP.

53:23.060 --> 53:25.494
SHE WAS ASLEEP
IN THE SUN PORCH.

53:25.500 --> 53:27.149
OH.

53:31.930 --> 53:34.319
IS THERE SOMETHING
YOU'D LIKE TO SAY TO ME, MOM ?

53:34.330 --> 53:35.820
NO.

53:37.900 --> 53:39.720
YES, YES, THERE IS.

53:41.100 --> 53:42.920
I'M ALL EARS.

53:42.930 --> 53:46.593
YOUR FATHER USED TO SAY THAT
TO ME ALL THE TIME,

53:46.600 --> 53:48.352
"I'M ALL EARS."

53:48.360 --> 53:51.693
SOMETIMES YOU
REMIND ME OF HIM.

53:53.200 --> 53:54.792
WHAT'S ON YOUR MIND ?

53:58.260 --> 54:00.649
YOU HAVE TO BE CAREFUL
WITH CHILDREN, DAVID,

54:00.660 --> 54:03.925
BECAUSE THEIR BLUEPRINTS
ARE STILL BEING DRAl-TED

54:03.930 --> 54:07.320
BY THE ADULTS IN THEIR LIVES
AND THIS LITTLE GIRL...

54:10.060 --> 54:11.925
WELL, IT SEEMS TO ME
THAT HER FOUNDATION

54:11.930 --> 54:15.149
IS PROBABLY UNSTABLE ENOUGH
WITHOUT YOU BRINGING YOUR...

54:16.630 --> 54:18.154
MY WHAT ?

54:18.160 --> 54:22.199
WELL, YOUR "RELATIONSHIP"
WITH HER UNCLE,

54:22.200 --> 54:23.724
YOU HAVE TO ADMIT,

54:23.730 --> 54:26.119
MIGHT BE A LITTLE CONFUSING
TO SOMEONE HER AGE.

54:27.400 --> 54:28.719
MOM...

54:31.760 --> 54:35.127
I'M HAPPY FOR YOU IF
THIS WHOLE PLAN THING OF YOURS

54:35.130 --> 54:37.690
HAS ENABLED YOU TO
"DRAl-T YOUR OWN BLUEPRINT"

54:37.700 --> 54:41.522
OR "PATCH UP SOME OF THE CRACKS
IN YOUR FOUNDATION", BUT...

54:41.530 --> 54:43.589
JUST BETWEEN
YOU AND ME,

54:43.600 --> 54:45.727
YOU'RE STARTING TO
SOUND LIKE A CRAZY PERSON.

54:47.660 --> 54:49.855
AND I THINK IT'S TIME
YOU KEPT THAT SHIT TO YOURSELF

54:49.860 --> 54:51.851
AND MINDED YOUR OWN
FUCKING BUSINESS.

54:59.730 --> 55:01.857
( door closing )

55:17.500 --> 55:19.229
THANK YOU.

55:32.330 --> 55:34.298
OKAY, IT'S A LITTLE WEIRD
DRIVING A DEAD GUY

55:34.300 --> 55:35.949
ALL THE WAY
BACK TO L.A.

55:35.960 --> 55:37.894
IT'S ONLY WEIRD
IF YOU MAKE IT WEIRD.

55:40.260 --> 55:41.852
IT'S A LITTLE WEIRD.

55:41.860 --> 55:44.192
IT'S NOT.

55:48.260 --> 55:50.854
YOU KNOW, NATE,
I DON'T KNOW WHY, BUT...

55:50.860 --> 55:52.327
IT'S COMFORTING TO KNOW

55:52.330 --> 55:54.298
YOU'RE JUST AS FUCKED UP
AS THE REST OF US.

55:54.300 --> 55:56.951
I'M NOT ANYWHERE NEAR AS
FUCKED UP AS THE REST OF YOU.

55:56.960 --> 55:58.222
YOU ARE.

55:58.230 --> 55:59.128
I'M NOT.

55:59.130 --> 56:01.621
YES, YOU ARE.

56:01.630 --> 56:03.222
SHUT UP AND DRIVE.

56:15.400 --> 56:18.927
YOU ARE MORE POWERFUL
